Hint / Approach
This is a 0/1 Knapsack variant — use a DP array where dp[s] stores the maximum profit achievable with allocation sum exactly equal to s. Initialize dp[0] = 0, all others to -∞. Traverse funds in order, update dp[s] from right to left.